h3#tooltip Tooltip
a(href="http://www.google.com/design/spec/components/tooltips.html")
  blockquote(cite="http://www.google.com/design/spec/components/tooltips.html") Tooltips are labels that appear on hover and focus when the user hovers over an element with the cursor, focuses on an element using a keyboard (usually through the tab key), or upon touch (without releasing) in a touch UI. They contain textual identification for the element in question. They may also contain brief helper text regarding the function of the element.
.card
  tabset
    tab
      tab-heading Demo
      .row
        .col.s12.l3
          p
            button(type="button", tooltip="helpful message").btn.btn-default Default
        .col.s12.l3
          p
            button(type="button", tooltip="finally", tooltip-popup-delay="500").btn.btn-default Delay
        .col.s12.l3
          p
            button(type="button", tooltip="mouseleave or click", tooltip-trigger="clickOff").btn.btn-default Click Off
        .col.s12.l3
          p Append To Body?
          .card
            .card-content
              button(type="button", tooltip="over", tooltip-append-to-body="true").btn.btn-default True
          .card
            .card-content
              button(type="button", tooltip="under").btn.btn-default False
    tab
      tab-heading HTML
      pre(prism).language-markup
        code(ng-non-bindable).language-markup
          :code
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col s12 l3">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" tooltip="helpful message">Default</button>
              </div>
              <div class="col s12 l3">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" tooltip="finally" tooltip-popup-delay="500">Delay</button>
              </div>
              <div class="col s12 l3">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" tooltip="mouseleave or click" tooltip-trigger="clickOff">Click Off</button>
              </div>
              <div class="col s12 l3">
                <p>Append To Body?</p>
                <div class="card">
                  <div class="card-content">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" tooltip="over" tooltip-append-to-body="true">True</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                  <div class="card-content">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" tooltip="under">False</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
